<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <%= image_tag "MarkNelson.jpg", width: 150, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9">
        <p>Program and project manager with substantial experience of organization change and transformation.</p>

        <p>Over 25 years experience in commercial and investment banking, asset management and commodities trading gained in the UK, Europe, the USA and Asia; working for financial institutions, corporates, software houses and consultancies.</p>

        <p>Specialties: Expertise includes business and IT strategy, process reengineering, data management, and program management. Experience includes cash and derivatives (equities, fixed income, FX, money markets, commodities), Finance, Treasury, Internal Audit and IT.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
        
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>